<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-10-06T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-10-06T00:00:00-05:00" n="990" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d990">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/16593.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Ambassador of Chile</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.<note n="46" xml:id="d990fn46">Similar acceptances from the other
                                conferees.</note>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of Chile</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-10-06">
                                    <hi rend="italic">October 6, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">My dear Mr. Secretary</hi>: I have not the least
                            objection to attending the meeting to which your excellency invites me
                            in your letter of yesterday, for the purpose of discussing the affairs
                            of Mexico, on Saturday the 9th of October at 2.30 p.m.</p>
                        <p>Cordially yours,</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Ed’o Suárez Mujica.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>